[Student "S"]
{NORTH has a pretty good hand, and when SOUTH shows \H support she naturally 
thinks about slam.

She has all four Aces but she wants to know about Kings. Unfortunately she can't start at 5NT because that 
has a different meaning, so she goes through the 4NT sequence even though she already knows the Ace answer.

Finding SOUTH with two Kings was what she wanted.}

