[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/blackwood"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST is just shy of a 2\C opening bid, and when EAST shows 13-15 points WEST 
wants to be in a slam.

WEST cannot use Blackwood because 4NT would be a natural invitation, but with EAST's latest bid 
being 2NT he can use Gerber.

Two Major Aces and two Minor Kings fill the holes in WEST's hand so he bids 7NT.}

